headline: Teradyne Declares Quarterly Cash Dividend
summary: NORTH READING, Mass., November 10, 2025--Teradyne, Inc. (NASDAQ:TER) today announced a quarterly cash dividend of $0.12 per share, payable on December 17, 2025, to shareholders of record as of the close of business on November 24, 2025.
